  <!-- EN: Sunblast furnace booster -->
  <Milira_SunBlasterBoosterJar.label>太阳熔炉增压罐</Milira_SunBlasterBoosterJar.label>
  <!-- EN: An auxiliary device that increases the fuel utilization rate of the Sunblast Furnace, thereby enhancing its operating speed. A single Sunblast Furnace can be connected to up to four boosters. -->
  <Milira_SunBlasterBoosterJar.description>能够增大太阳熔炉的燃料利用率，从而增加工作速度的辅助装置。一座太阳熔炉最多可以连接4个增压罐。</Milira_SunBlasterBoosterJar.description>
  
